<div id="review_1431385809" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1431385809" />
    <a title="Olga therebelreader" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/24443337-olga-therebelreader"><img alt="Olga therebelreader" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1540920390p2/24443337.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1431385809?book_show_action=true">Nov 02, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Olga therebelreader" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Olga therebelreader" href="/user/show/24443337-olga-therebelreader">Olga therebelreader</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/24443337-olga-therebelreader?shelf=twisted">twisted</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/24443337-olga-therebelreader?shelf=romance">romance</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/24443337-olga-therebelreader?shelf=highly-emotional">highly-emotional</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/24443337-olga-therebelreader?shelf=suspense-angst">suspense-angst</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/24443337-olga-therebelreader?shelf=dark-erotica">dark-erotica</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1431385809" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1322230131513286824">This is my first Lucian Bane read and I have to say, his writing is amazing. This book was more unsettling than I expected. The story is creepy, maddening, mind-blowing, heartbreaking, haunting, disturbing, mysterious, blowingly erotic all at once, and I loved it!!<br/><br/>Chaos is a sad, lost soul who has never received love. And if she has never received love, how can she love others? <br/><br/><br/><a href='http://s1379.photobucket.com/user/Olga_NNikolaidi/media/a776a34da0ec8ac4531a7b8cee9921da_zpsqwahqhqg.jpg.html' target='_blank' rel='nofollow noopener'>
  <img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1451288609i/17525040._SY540_.jpg' alt=' photo a776a34da0ec8ac4531a7b8cee9921da_zpsqwahqhqg.jpg' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/>
</a><br/><br/><br/>Solomon has his own secrets. He is a lone wolf who thinks that love has forgotten him. He deeply loved a woman once</span>
  <span id="freeText1322230131513286824" style="display:none">This is my first Lucian Bane read and I have to say, his writing is amazing. This book was more unsettling than I expected. The story is creepy, maddening, mind-blowing, heartbreaking, haunting, disturbing, mysterious, blowingly erotic all at once, and I loved it!!<br><br>Chaos is a sad, lost soul who has never received love. And if she has never received love, how can she love others? <br><br><br><a href="http://s1379.photobucket.com/user/Olga_NNikolaidi/media/a776a34da0ec8ac4531a7b8cee9921da_zpsqwahqhqg.jpg.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">
  <img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1451288609i/17525040._SY540_.jpg" alt=" photo a776a34da0ec8ac4531a7b8cee9921da_zpsqwahqhqg.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg">
</a><br><br><br>Solomon has his own secrets. He is a lone wolf who thinks that love has forgotten him. He deeply loved a woman once but now he has condemned himself to loneliness and emotional relinquishment. <br><br><br><a href="http://s1379.photobucket.com/user/Olga_NNikolaidi/media/large_zps539kjo8o.jpg.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">
  <img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1451346365i/17529715._SY540_.jpg" alt=" photo large_zps539kjo8o.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg">
</a><br><br><br>But, sweet Chaos makes his blood boil. Solomon will eventually prove her that she is capable to love and feel love, and that she can abandon herself and her logical reasoning in the name of love.<br><br><a href="http://s1379.photobucket.com/user/Olga_NNikolaidi/media/879c58c74e4eb38c2d5464eec8fbfe3e_zpsy5aayhmj.gif.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">
  <img src="https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1451346365ra/17529716.gif" alt=" photo 879c58c74e4eb38c2d5464eec8fbfe3e_zpsy5aayhmj.gif" class="gr-hostedUserImg">
</a><br><br>This is worth picking up and reading. It was a brilliant read, something very different and thought provoking and I look forward to reading more of Lucian Bane’s books.<br><br><a href="http://s1379.photobucket.com/user/Olga_NNikolaidi/media/joe_manganiello_wink_zpsekiuw7po.gif.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">
  <img src="https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1451346365ra/17529717.gif" alt=" photo joe_manganiello_wink_zpsekiuw7po.gif" class="gr-hostedUserImg">
</a><br><br></span>
