<div id="review_1398484134" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1398484134" />
    <a title="Alicia Huckleby" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/43292549-alicia-huckleby"><img alt="Alicia Huckleby" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1438900027p2/43292549.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1398484134?book_show_action=true">Sep 22, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Alicia Huckleby" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Alicia Huckleby" href="/user/show/43292549-alicia-huckleby">Alicia Huckleby</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1398484134" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10827888989797692881">A beautifully twisted tale full of romance, suspense, and dash of heart pounding horror! <br/>Travel into the dark mind of Lucian Bane thru the eyes of Solomon and Chaos. <br/>A slow burning fire builds from the beginning between our love birds in this riveting read, their romance story unlike any other you will ever have the pleasure of indulging yourself in! Solomon is sexy, full of compassion , heart, faith and wit while our heroine Chaos is the quiet, introverted ignorant ( and I don&apos;t mean that rudel</span>
  <span id="freeText10827888989797692881" style="display:none">A beautifully twisted tale full of romance, suspense, and dash of heart pounding horror! <br />Travel into the dark mind of Lucian Bane thru the eyes of Solomon and Chaos. <br />A slow burning fire builds from the beginning between our love birds in this riveting read, their romance story unlike any other you will ever have the pleasure of indulging yourself in! Solomon is sexy, full of compassion , heart, faith and wit while our heroine Chaos is the quiet, introverted ignorant ( and I don't mean that rudely) victim of a religious cult jumping straight out of something resembling Children of the Corn! And that one scene ( which I won't spoil), left me staring with my mouth hanging wide open. You will definitely never find another narrative that even comes close to Desecrating Solomon! <br />Master is a piece of work in himself, the classic villain we love to hate. He's a man with no mercy and filled to the brim with evil intentions. And what he wants to do with our Hero and Heroine does not include an invitation to dinner. Well...maybe it does, I guess we will have to see!<br /><br />Bane leisurely lures the reader in and just when you feel like its time to turn back, he's already got his claws in you! His descriptive ability blows my imagination clean out of the water. And although I'm a fan of suspense/mystery/horror this tale had me reading with the lamp on in the last 20%. But damn that spine tingling feeling hurt so good!! <br />I waited quite awhile for Desecrating Solomon to make an appearance and not only did Bane not disappoint but he rocked my socks off!! This book is one of my favorites for 2015 and has placed itself into Alicia's list of books she likes to reread!! I'll be waiting impatiently to see Lucian's next creation!</span>
  <a data-text-id="10827888989797692881" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


