<div id="review_1422821308" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1422821308" />
    <a title="Danielle Fulton" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/31378028-danielle-fulton"><img alt="Danielle Fulton" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1438614678p2/31378028.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1422821308?book_show_action=true">Oct 22, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Danielle Fulton" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Danielle Fulton" href="/user/show/31378028-danielle-fulton">Danielle Fulton</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/27257192-desecrating-solomon">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/31378028-danielle-fulton?shelf=favorite">favorite</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/31378028-danielle-fulton?shelf=series">series</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/31378028-danielle-fulton?shelf=best-indie-author">best-indie-author</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/31378028-danielle-fulton?shelf=dark">dark</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/31378028-danielle-fulton?shelf=adult-fiction">adult-fiction</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1422821308" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11303075929900229972"><strong>Terrifyingly Brilliant</strong><br/><br/>Oh my, where to start? What a freaking crazy ride through a brilliant writers scary mind! <br/>Solomon and Chaos oh what twisted scary plans are ahead for you?<br/>A story that brings you through heartache, terror, mind control, confusion, shock, disgust, hope, love and so much more. Lucian manages to show some real evilness as well as lessons in love and overcoming your past and fears. <br/>To bad Solomon has only just begun to realize what absolute crazy is in this scary as shiz town. I</span>
  <span id="freeText11303075929900229972" style="display:none"><strong>Terrifyingly Brilliant</strong><br /><br />Oh my, where to start? What a freaking crazy ride through a brilliant writers scary mind! <br />Solomon and Chaos oh what twisted scary plans are ahead for you?<br />A story that brings you through heartache, terror, mind control, confusion, shock, disgust, hope, love and so much more. Lucian manages to show some real evilness as well as lessons in love and overcoming your past and fears. <br />To bad Solomon has only just begun to realize what absolute crazy is in this scary as shiz town. I love him with the crotchety Miss Mary such a great relationship and how he manages to overcome lost love and care again but will they live to enjoy it? Chaos is such a strong yet achingly fragile somehow still innocent character you just ache for her. What this poor girl has endured is nauseating and you feel it so much that you just want to protect her yourself and do horrible things to Master!!<br />Lucian has brought us to a new level with this book and it's scary as crap asylum and cult and addictive story.<br />I could not put this story down at all,I read it in one sitting and oh Lucian what a way to leave us hanging you cruel man!! Oh what creepily amazing stories you weave!!! <br />A standing ovation from me!</span>
  <a data-text-id="11303075929900229972" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
