<span id="freeTextContainer10685502788163510311"><strong>Mind Blowing </strong><br/><br/>This book needs more than five stars. Mr. Bane does it again and brings the boom to this story. You will get drawn in from the beginning and hooked till the very end. The raw emotions you will feel, along with the chills. The emotions are real and makes you feel as your experiencing them with the characters. <br/><br/>This is a dark romance and some parts may hit home to some that experienced parts of the story. I cried, I felt, got mad, sad, happy through out this whole story. I connected wi</span>
  <span id="freeText10685502788163510311" style="display:none"><strong>Mind Blowing </strong><br /><br />This book needs more than five stars. Mr. Bane does it again and brings the boom to this story. You will get drawn in from the beginning and hooked till the very end. The raw emotions you will feel, along with the chills. The emotions are real and makes you feel as your experiencing them with the characters. <br /><br />This is a dark romance and some parts may hit home to some that experienced parts of the story. I cried, I felt, got mad, sad, happy through out this whole story. I connected with the story but with the characters also. All the pain and suffering comes with love good and bad. A love that builds and gets stronger. <br /><br />Solomon &amp; Chaos story will take you on a journey that's just beginning. Two people that don't know each other, come together and learn. The town they live in has a curse and it's time for the curse to end. Only its not that simple and there are battles that will be faced. <br /><br />Amazing job Lucian on another amazing book. A must read for sure. I can't wait for the next book in the series and sure hope you plan on writing that really soon ;-) I need to know what happens.</span>
  <a data-text-id="10685502788163510311" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

