        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1398426340" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5456779045171922772">I have read all of Lucian Banes books, so going into this one I knew it was going to be a great one. But I was wrong, this book, for me, was beyond anything I could have imagined! Once I started reading it, it was near impossible to put down. This story is so well written that it grabbed me and pulled me right in. It evoked feelings of rage for &quot;master&quot; ...deep compassion and understanding for Silence and profound admiration for Solomon. I experienced a lot of emotions while reading this book fr</span>
  <span id="freeText5456779045171922772" style="display:none">I have read all of Lucian Banes books, so going into this one I knew it was going to be a great one. But I was wrong, this book, for me, was beyond anything I could have imagined! Once I started reading it, it was near impossible to put down. This story is so well written that it grabbed me and pulled me right in. It evoked feelings of rage for "master" ...deep compassion and understanding for Silence and profound admiration for Solomon. I experienced a lot of emotions while reading this book from laughing to sadness, hatred, fear, anticipation and love just to name a few. Being a "dark" book, I know bad things happen, but even that has no comparison to the twist and turns I did not see coming! This book is haunting and terrifying and mysterious, I was left dealing with shock of what I just read. Trying to piece together what is going on, who, why, how...I found myself asking these questions. I was turning the pages absorbing the information, wanting desperately to find those answers! This story is just getting started and I can't wait to discover what is in store for us in the next two books! Hurry, hurry pleeeease!! <br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="5456779045171922772" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
