  <span id="freeText3607328827868404295" style="display:none">Oh my, where to start? What a freaking crazy ride through a brilliant writers scary mind!<br />Solomon and Chaos oh what twisted scary plans are ahead for you?<br />A story that brings you through heartache, terror, mind control, confusion, shock, disgust, hope, love and so much more. Lucian manages to show some real evilness as well as lessons in love and overcoming your past and fears.<br />To bad Solomon has only just begun to realize what absolute crazy is in this scary as shiz town. I love him with the crotchety Miss Mary such a great relationship and how he manages to overcome lost love and care again but will they live to enjoy it? Chaos is such a strong yet achingly fragile somehow still innocent character you just ache for her. What this poor girl has endured is nauseating and you feel it so much that you just want to protect her yourself and do horrible things to Master!!<br />Lucian has brought us to a new level with this book and it's scary as crap asylum and cult and addictive story.<br />I could not put this story down at all,I read it in one sitting and oh Lucian what a way to leave us hanging you cruel man!! Oh what creepily amazing stories you weave!!!<br />A standing ovation from me!</span>
