<span id="freeTextContainer11089945286939154213">Unpredictable. Unexpected. Dark with a surprising twist. That&apos;s only the surface of Desecrating Solomon. Just when you think you know where the story is going Lucian Bane whips your head around with a &quot;what the hell just happened?&quot;<br/>It is a well written story with characters like Solomon and Chaos who you are rooting for and others like Master and Grandmother that you just want to banish to hell. And the dark theme and secrets are always underlying throughout the tale.<br/>Desecrating Solomon is captiv</span>
  <span id="freeText11089945286939154213" style="display:none">Unpredictable. Unexpected. Dark with a surprising twist. That's only the surface of Desecrating Solomon. Just when you think you know where the story is going Lucian Bane whips your head around with a "what the hell just happened?"<br />It is a well written story with characters like Solomon and Chaos who you are rooting for and others like Master and Grandmother that you just want to banish to hell. And the dark theme and secrets are always underlying throughout the tale.<br />Desecrating Solomon is captivating and really kept me on the edge of my seat wondering what was coming next......and now I have to wait for the next book to find out!!!<br />You can't go wrong with a Lucian Bane book.....especially this one!</span>
