<span id="freeTextContainer15505788318024650972">My Review of Desocrating Solomon by Lucian Bane<br/>My Rating 5 Rock your World Stars!<br/><br/>Have you ever read a book that made you feel as if you were watching it in slow motion? That’s how I feel after finishing this book. I feel as if I visited the depths of hell alongside of these characters.<br/>Mr. Bane has a brilliant way of telling you a story you know has lessons to be learned while reading. This is an intense read Interesting characters, some you like and others you wish would find their path to hell </span>
  <span id="freeText15505788318024650972" style="display:none">My Review of Desocrating Solomon by Lucian Bane<br />My Rating 5 Rock your World Stars!<br /><br />Have you ever read a book that made you feel as if you were watching it in slow motion? That’s how I feel after finishing this book. I feel as if I visited the depths of hell alongside of these characters.<br />Mr. Bane has a brilliant way of telling you a story you know has lessons to be learned while reading. This is an intense read Interesting characters, some you like and others you wish would find their path to hell first.<br />Solomon is this compassionate man filled with so much heart, whom meets Chaos who is a woman withdrawn into herself, an introvert of sorts but, this is a very strong woman to have endured what she has and survive it.Oh, Lordy! The old lady Mary, whom I just loved in this story. I would love to befriend someone like her.<br />The Master is one you hope will find his path to hell and you’ll enjoy watching him make the trip.<br />This twisted tale of romance is not like anything I’ve ever read and I’m learning the more of Lucian Bane’s books I read all have a twist and something to be learned while reading. This is truly one of those books that captures you grips you so tightly that you unable to quit reading until you hit the finish line. “And” even still can’t wait for more.<br />I loved the suspense, and intrigue, the hold your breath moments.<br />Lucian is a master of words, creating these worlds that take us away and have us living his characters story. As always the experience is worth the journey you’ll take when reading, which I highly recommend you do.<br />Thank you, Lucian for another outstanding book. You should be so proud It’s Amazing!<br /><br /></span>
