<div id="review_1400079033" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1400079033" />
    <a title="Nichole Watson" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/38616357-nichole-watson"><img alt="Nichole Watson" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1555286424p2/38616357.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1400079033?book_show_action=true">Sep 24, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Nichole Watson" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Nichole Watson" href="/user/show/38616357-nichole-watson">Nichole Watson</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/38616357-nichole-watson?shelf=adult-fiction">adult-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/38616357-nichole-watson?shelf=best-dark-erotica">best-dark-erotica</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/38616357-nichole-watson?shelf=best-erotica">best-erotica</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/38616357-nichole-watson?shelf=best-indie-author">best-indie-author</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/38616357-nichole-watson?shelf=dark">dark</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/38616357-nichole-watson?shelf=dark-erotica">dark-erotica</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/38616357-nichole-watson?shelf=erotic-action-and-adventure">erotic-action-and-adventure</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/38616357-nichole-watson?shelf=erotic-mystery-thriller">erotic-mystery-thriller</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/38616357-nichole-watson?shelf=erotic-suspense">erotic-suspense</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/38616357-nichole-watson?shelf=erotic-thriller">erotic-thriller</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1400079033" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14210345696489328106">Do you remember lying in your bed as a kid where every creak of the floor boards and wrapping of a tree branch outside your window was the boogy man coming to get you? That state of fear crippling you and taking over your body, that is close to the feels you will have while experiencing the world that Solomon and Chaos exist in.<br/>These beautifully broken, uniquely complex and puzzling characters will leave your heart breaking and your mind spinning. You will want to scream, cry, and fight for Solo</span>
  <span id="freeText14210345696489328106" style="display:none">Do you remember lying in your bed as a kid where every creak of the floor boards and wrapping of a tree branch outside your window was the boogy man coming to get you? That state of fear crippling you and taking over your body, that is close to the feels you will have while experiencing the world that Solomon and Chaos exist in.<br />These beautifully broken, uniquely complex and puzzling characters will leave your heart breaking and your mind spinning. You will want to scream, cry, and fight for Solomon and Chaos. A story where your fight or flight reaction will be engaged during the entire digestion of each written word.<br />The vividly painted scenes will make you feel as though you could reach out and run your hand in the fur of the wolf, have you panting and out of breath with Solomon as he searches the woods. The words will wrap themselves around you like a vine, entangling and encompassing your very being. The twists within the storyline are like walking in the woods that surround Solomon's home deep, dark, mysterious but addicting and amazingly wonderful.<br />If you have read other works by Lucian Bane you will not be disappointed with the story of Solomon. Unlike any of his other stories this was a delicious surprise and something I am glad to have read. Now I wait and want like so many others for more of this epic tale.</span>
  <a data-text-id="14210345696489328106" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


